#-Function--editorsyntaxstring
  Function: editorsyntaxstring
      Desc: Return full path and arguments to edit a text file.
          : Only editors 'joe' and 'nano' are supported at the moment.
  Synopsis: editorsyntaxstring filetype filename
    Source: /usr/share/okusi/entities/scripts/archive/srcarchive/entities.d/files/filetype/textfiletype.bash
